<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/wallace-collection> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Wallace Collection is a national museum in an historic London town house. In 25 galleries, unsurpassed French 18th-century painting (including Old Masters), furniture, porcelain and a world class armoury are on display. Wallace Collection is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Culture, Media and Sport ."@en .
